sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as ODH Model Controller<br/>Leader-Elected Pod
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant IstioCP as Istio Control Plane<br/>15012/TCP gRPC mTLS
    participant Authorino as Authorino<br/>AuthConfig Processor
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>9090/TCP HTTP
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>Route Handler

    Note over User,Router: Flow 1: InferenceService Creation (Serverless Mode with Service Mesh)

    User->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService<br/>Auth: OIDC/ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Event: InferenceService Created<br/>Watch Cache Update

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create OpenShift Route<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Router: Route Created Event

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create VirtualService<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>IstioCP: VirtualService Created Event

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update Gateway (shared)<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>IstioCP: Gateway Updated Event

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMeshMember<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create PeerAuthentication<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>IstioCP: PeerAuth Created Event

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Telemetry<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>IstioCP: Telemetry Created Event

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create AuthConfig<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Authorino: AuthConfig Created Event

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over User,Router: Flow 2: Knative Service Validation (Webhook)

    User->>K8sAPI: Create/Update Knative Service<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: OIDC/ServiceAccount
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-serving-knative-dev-v1-service<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS (service-ca)<br/>Auth: Kubernetes API
    Webhook->>Webhook: Validate Service Mesh Integration<br/>Check Istio sidecar configuration
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation Response<br/>Allow/Deny with message
    K8sAPI-->>User: Admission Decision

    Note over User,Router: Flow 3: Monitoring Integration

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create/Update ServiceMonitor<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Prometheus->>Controller: Scrape /metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTPS (internal CA)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)
    Controller-->>Prometheus: Metrics Response<br/>Controller and InferenceService metrics

    Note over User,Router: Flow 4: Storage Secret Management

    User->>K8sAPI: Create Secret with storage config<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>S3/PVC credentials
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Event: Secret Created<br/>Watch Cache Update
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceAccount<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Mount Secret to InferenceService<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over User,Router: Flow 5: ModelMesh Mode

    User->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService (ModelMesh mode)<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Event: InferenceService Created
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create OpenShift Route<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Service<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceAccount<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ClusterRoleBinding<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    K8sAPI-->>User: Resources Created
